Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:09.39,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:11.42,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I always keep my promises
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:13.20,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,since I'm a businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:18.81,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,That's a good attitude, Mr. Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:21.84,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,I'd like to start discussing the deal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:22.93,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,Is that okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:24.62,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Before we begin,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:28.13,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,please refrain from smoking in my presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:34.52,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Second-hand smoke contains a higher amount of toxic substances than direct smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:43.46,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,The amount of the carcinogen dimethylnitrosamine present in direct smoke is between 5.3 and 43 nanograms,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:48.15,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,while there are between 680 and 823 nanograms in second-hand smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:53.01,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, the amount of quinoline from second-hand smoke is eleven times greater than direct smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:56.05,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,A staggering eighteen thousand nanograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:01:02.04,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,In other words, the health risk of people exposed to second-hand smoke is greater than those who actually smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:06.03,DTB-Default,Thug A,0,0,0,,Hold your breath, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.00,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Let's pretend we never met.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.08,0:01:13.33,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:17.21,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:23.40,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.39,0:01:37.36,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,This is only a down payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:43.62,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Once I've confirmed its authenticity, I'll pay double.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:47.74,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with it once it's in your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:52.63,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I'll start by killing off about three thousand employees from our rival company.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:55.60,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:57.97,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I'll resell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:00.25,DTB-Default,Thug B,0,0,0,,Bastard, don't screw around with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:08.39,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,Is it really that valuable?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:10.40,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.65,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,The deal is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:16.84,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:23.03,DTB-Default,Thug A,0,0,0,,If the boss says the deal is off, the deal is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:26.66,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I suppose it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:31.43,DTB-Default,Thug A,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.56,DTB-Default,Thug A,0,0,0,,My arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:52.71,DTB-Default,Thug A,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.38,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,Hey, get a hold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:09.75,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're a...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.50,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,contractor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:18.42,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,Stay away! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:19.97,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.96,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,Hey, my feet... I can't move my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:38.25,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.67,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,Stay away, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:55.66,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Its location.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:58.25,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,I'll talk... I'll talk, so don't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:01.55,DTB-Default,Kingpin,0,0,0,,2220 Pier Drive... it's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:04.48,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,That's a good attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:52.33,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,Your remuneration is anything but impressive, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:08.88,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:26.17,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,You're Havoc, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:41.96,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,You'll be accompanying us for the next several months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.63,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,From your right: April,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.01,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,July,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:49.22,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,and myself, November 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.47,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,We're from MI6.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:04.17,Location,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fs60\pos(640,566)\c&HE2E4E5&}Tokyo International Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.46,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,She goes by the alias of Havoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:12.30,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,She was feared by people as the most diabolical contractor in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:17.41,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,It was said that the number of lives she claimed during the Third South American War, also known as Heaven's War,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:21.92,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,was anywhere between several hundred and several thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:27.05,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,She has the ability to create a vacuum at any location,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.68,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,but the details are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:33.87,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,Her ability has not been confirmed as of five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:39.19,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,She is currently considered a regressor, as indicated by a spectrum analysis of her star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:41.86,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,Regressor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:44.36,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,You don't hear much about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:47.54,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,Cases like that aren't only rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:54.08,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,Once their activities become untraceable, the subject is usually removed from further investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.56,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,And moved into research, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:57.81,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:07:59.00,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:06.61,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,It was reported that the subject admitted to being partially involved with the CIA during the MI6 interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:10.93,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,The CIA has bluntly denied those allegations, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:17.15,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,I am Eric Nishijima from Pandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:19.90,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,I'm here to ask you several questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:25.45,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,When you disembarked from the airplane, did you experience any physical abnormalities?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:27.79,DTB-Default,Havoc,0,0,0,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:29.96,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,How about mentally?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:32.02,DTB-Default,Havoc,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:37.42,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,From this point forward, you will cooperate with Pandora, the U.N.-led research institute,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:41.37,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,in conducting various experiments within Hell's Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:43.09,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Do you have any problems regarding this arrangement?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:47.81,DTB-Default,Havoc,0,0,0,,You're the ones who have a problem with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:05.67,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,The downfall of a contractor, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:10.82,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Five years ago, after the disappearance of Heaven's Gate in South America,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:16.18,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,how did she wander about and arrive in Romania?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:20.96,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:26.18,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:32.40,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I am Jack Simon of the British Foreign Ministry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:35.31,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I've been informed about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:36.52,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:39.10,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Please call me Jack, Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:44.94,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,My name is Kirihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:51.58,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode Five Red Giant over Eastern Europe... (Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:08.44,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,Is this your first time in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:14.44,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,No, I've been here twice before on assassination missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:17.74,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:23.93,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Mr. Simon, I also have something I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.00,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Ask away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:32.03,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Upon capturing a valuable subject such as Havoc, why didn't the MI6
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:37.70,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,conduct research of their own, instead of deferring her to the U.N.-led Pandora?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:40.30,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Isn't it the same in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:44.83,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Although new international laws were established after the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:50.01,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I can't believe nations have given up on researching supernatural beings and the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:51.80,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Japan included.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:52.71,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:56.43,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,In the U.K., there is very little public support for research on supernatural beings,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:11:01.11,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,especially after the impasse that occurred in South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:06.31,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,In order to avoid risk and efficiently obtain information,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:10.11,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,we have concluded that it is in our best interests to follow standard procedures.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:18.63,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I did advise them to have her killed off for her own sake or have her return to her life as a prostitute, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:26.95,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:28.89,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.07,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:36.44,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:38.29,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Kouno?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:44.92,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,Boss, it seems like there's an organization trying to approach the helicopter transporting Havoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:46.26,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:48.79,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,They're talking about it in the back of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.95,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:12:01.18,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,We transferred it to Pandora to prevent it from becoming proprietary property, yet the CIA...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:04.25,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter. Kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:07.47,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I'll have Inspector Kirihara take care of the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.73,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I'm going to stop the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:16.01,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Kouno, Matsumoto-san, confirm the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:18.10,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Saitou, contact the division manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:22.54,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Tell him to issue a warning to the CIA through diplomatic routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:23.62,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:28.20,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I want an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:35.17,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Explanation? The CIA came to retrieve her at the very last moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:38.40,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,unaware that they fell for our bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:39.34,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Bluff?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:43.27,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Yes, she's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:47.68,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.72,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,How cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.35,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,That aside, since when...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:57.46,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,It's not that I don't trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:13:02.11,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,I just wanted to know how much information would be leaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.60,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,My sincere apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:14.75,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Where are we passing by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:18.17,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Rest assured, we're heading toward Pandora headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.54,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.23,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,That is... a person just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:41.14,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,There isn't anyone around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:42.78,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,I'm sure there was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:48.41,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.25,DTB-Default,July,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:00.70,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:01.88,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,Mr. Simon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:03.24,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,We're still in the middle of a convoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:05.15,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Apparently we fell into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:05.97,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,Trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:23.86,DTB-Default,Havoc,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.60,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:29.49,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,That's the person who ran by the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:35.12,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.12,DTB-Default,Havoc,0,0,0,,The black Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:52.38,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:56.35,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,Boss, they're contractors!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:50.17,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Headquarters! Headquarters, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.63,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Call for assistance immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:11.39,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:16.47,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Focus on retrieving the abducted Havoc for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:18.44,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:20.75,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Do you think you can resolve the issue that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:24.83,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,I didn't expect the additional information would be leaked as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:29.21,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Japanese police have no administrative control over confidential information,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:32.44,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,just as November 11 said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:35.01,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,November 11?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:39.94,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Jack Simon's code name, the diplomat who accompanied you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:41.79,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Then he's the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:45.54,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,The top agent from MI6.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:52.09,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,In any case, as stated in Pandora Law, Article 22,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:57.16,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,you are to retrieve Havoc according to our instructions from this point forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.47,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:16:59.88,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.22,0:17:04.10,Location,,0,0,0,,{\be1\bord0\shad0\pos(645,471)\fax-0.18\frz8.959\frx0\fry356\fnArial\c&H000000&\b0}Public Safety Division\N\N\N\N\N\N\NForeign Affairs Department 4
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:04.10,Location,,0,0,0,,{\be2\bord0\shad0\pos(645,473)\fax-0.18\frz8.959\frx0\fry356\fnArial\c&HFFFFFF&\b0}Public Safety Division\N\N\N\N\N\N\NForeign Affairs Department 4
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:07.91,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,I don't care if he's a triple A agent. He was outsmarted as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:10.11,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,He's not that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:14.59,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,Isn't there a possibility that they let her be abducted?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:16.38,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,Why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:18.62,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,If I knew why, I wouldn't be asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:24.50,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,Boss, a notice from the Division of Astronomy just came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:30.48,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,Activity from BK201 was detected at the time you were attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:34.03,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,BK201...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:56.19,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Contractors sure have a troublesome life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:18:00.95,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,They have to smoke tobacco and drink liquor against their will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:03.73,DTB-Default,April,0,0,0,,I like alcohol though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:09.50,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Did you know everything was going to turn out like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:11.09,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,November 11?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:16.59,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,If I had known, I would have taken all precautionary measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:20.97,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,However, my measures were insufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:23.96,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,In other words, the answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:30.19,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,However, from this incident, one thing's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:37.10,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,No diplomatic route can dissuade the organization that abducted Havoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:38.55,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.66,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,The enemy isn't the CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:46.23,DTB-Default,July,0,0,0,,Shinjuku Torino Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:48.49,DTB-Default,July,0,0,0,,Parking available.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:50.25,DTB-Default,July,0,0,0,,Shinjuku Torino Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:52.46,DTB-Default,July,0,0,0,,Parking available.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:55.76,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:19:00.09,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Next time, it'll be our turn to hunt him down...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:04.17,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Mr. 201BK.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:19.70,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,She's calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:22.79,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I don't see anything out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:24.76,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.73,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,We'll deliver her to the syndicate tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:39.47,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,It seems that they want to keep Havoc away from the gate at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:45.22,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Even I don't want to keep a monster like that around for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:48.37,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Monster, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:57.24,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hey, where the hell is Havoc?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:59.66,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,I don't see Hei either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:01.22,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Yin, where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:02.95,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,They left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:04.31,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Left?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:04.95,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:07.67,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.86,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Who would have thought you'd still be alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:22.84,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Carmine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:26.21,DTB-Default,Havoc,0,0,0,,It's been a while since someone called me by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:30.11,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What happened during that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:35.41,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Where's my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:37.71,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Where's Pai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:42.31,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,You call out your sister's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:46.61,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,It drifts into the air and disappears into the crimson sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:48.49,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,A regressor,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:53.67,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,deprived of power in exchange for momentary peace and a fragment of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:58.97,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,However, sins take their toll and deny everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:04.65,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The cold blade cuts proof that the corpse from that day once lived,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:08.35,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,and the gates of hell have been knocked on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:09.34,Title,,0,0,0,,{\c&He3e3e3&}Episode Six Red Giant over Eastern Europe... (Part Two)